# So the sum of all the factorials of the digits of the number is:

# 5 + 1 + 8 + 4 + 0 + 3 + 2 + 8 + 0 = 30

# What is the sum of all the factorials of the digits of the number 100! ?

def factorial(n)
  if n == 0
    1
  else
    n * factorial(n-1)
  end
end

def factorial_sum(n)
  n.to_s.chars.map(&:to_i).map { |i| factorial(i) }.reduce(:+)
end

p factorial_sum(100)
